data.name: XCollator
desc: provides locale-sensitive collation algorithms for string comparison.

methods.name: compareString
desc: Compare 2 strings in specific locale and algorithm.

methods.name: compareSubstring
desc: Compare 2 substrings in specific locale and algorithm.

methods.name: listCollatorAlgorithms
desc: List all collator algorithms for a given locale.

methods.name: listCollatorOptions
desc: List all end user collator options for a given algorithm.

methods.name: loadCollatorAlgorithm
desc: Load a particular collator algorithm for the locale.

methods.name: loadCollatorAlgorithmWithEndUserOption
desc: Load a collator algorithm with options chosen by end user.

methods.name: loadDefaultCollator
desc: Load the collator with default algorithm defined in locale data.
